-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyoMeWZ8.png&h=204a6ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8WBVGrP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8WBVGrP.png&h=7f13ed29&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nh0fGrP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNh0fGrP.png&h=adac79b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p6Rq3Fa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp6Rq3Fa.png&h=b8319742&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z1vrN6R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ1vrN6R.png&h=a0922cbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NcRCamw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNcRCamw.png&h=bb4e826e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbqbZeR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbqbZeR.png&h=e19e867f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[最新公告]（截至7月31日10:30pm）</span><br />\n<br />\n&quot;[銀行業]香港金融同路人&quot;TG谷一共有4,020名谷友，<br />\n&quot;香港金融同路人&quot;TG谷一共有1,766名谷友，<br />\n<br />\n並收到769位銀行/金融從業員以職員證表達訴求，願意於8月5日加入香港大三罷行動。<br />\n<br />\n兩個TG群組投票顯示總共有過千位金融界人士回覆8月1日會來快閃遮打花園！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">數字持續增加中！<br />\n</span></span> 但未有時間統計最新數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n*以下為參與者所屬之香港各大銀行及金融機構列表，暫時已經<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">有來自79間金融同業響應今次活動</span></span>*<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B5kZ8cA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB5kZ8cA.png&h=aa8e21de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FdK0SEg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFdK0SEg.png&h=2a813a0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eAhUW5X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeAhUW5X.png&h=de5c8ee3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">*以是參與者個人意見，不代表所屬公司之立場</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">關於今晚8月1日快閃遮打花園詳情：</span></span><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1389422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1389422</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加入我們吧！ 與香港人共同進退！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［銀行業］金融業同路人：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MNo3GlhMU9KckMjtP84rXw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMNo3GlhMU9KckMjtP84rXw&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5wEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=a49a1c4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MNo3GlhMU9KckMjtP84rXw</a><br />\n<br />\nFor 所有金融業同路人：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkfinancefellow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkfinancefellow&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5wEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=c6b8ab15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkfinancefellow</a>"},{"pid":"f01150ba547fe0f8c5c99f71a5ea78beb751b1d1","tid":1393052,"uid":1673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:13:12.000Z","msg":"正評是必須的"},{"pid":"15b0db9356ae4e0081ea521ce69c80083873dbe7","tid":1393052,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b2a781fd736b1c554a336050f10798f4afa7ab","tid":1393052,"uid":34293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:15:21.000Z","msg":"革命無罪  造反有理"},{"pid":"040e0e57f886acc41b56c6a1a29bf4ccaee6343c","tid":1393052,"uid":268066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:15:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c403f357c0c4df4e3019c07b026ff09a82217c34","tid":1393052,"uid":254653,